=Description=

"Gnusha is an open source hardware co-op built around the
idea of leveraging, channeling and focusing the activiity of members
in hackerspaces and fablabs. Machines/equipment operated in local
shops can run a profit, some money goes back into local overhead, and
the rest goes back into the co-op for self-improvement: building
better machines, enhancing performance."

